('ONET-WELDING_SOLDERING_AND_BRAZING_MACHINE_SETTERS_OP', 'source_onet_welding_soldering_and_brazing_machine_setters_operators_and_tenders', 'Welding, Soldering, and Brazing Machine Setters, Operators, and Tenders', 'Welding, Soldering, and Brazing Machine Setters, Operators, and Tenders is an imported ONET role/occupation concept. It needs TALLENTIN normalization before production routing.', 'role_title', 'Set up, operate, or tend welding, soldering, or brazing machines or robots that weld, braze, solder, or heat treat metal products, components, or assemblies. Includes workers who operate laser cutters or laser-beam machines.', ARRAY['Aluminum Welder','Arc and Gas Welder','Arc Welding Machine Operator','Billet Assembler','Braze Operator','Brazing Machine Operator','Brazing Machine Setter','Brazing Machine Setter Operator','Brazing Machine Setup Operator','Brazing Machine Tender','Builder','Certified Welder','Controlled Atmospheric Furnace Brazer','Electron Beam Machine Welder Setter','Electron Beam Welder Setter','Electron Beam Welding Machine Operator','Electroslag Welding Machine Operator','Explosion Welder','Fabrication Specialist','Fabricator','Field Operator','Field Technician (Field Tech)','Finishing Technician (Finishing Tech)','Friction Welding Machine Operator','Furnace Brazer','Gas Welding Machine Operator','Induction Brazer','Induction Heating Equipment Setter','Industrial Welder','Laser Beam Machine Operator','Laser Operator','Machine Burner','Machine Operator','Machine Welder','Manufacturing Associate','Manufacturing Operator','Mig Welder','Mill Operator','Oxygraph Operator','Racking Machine Operator','Racking Technician (Racking Tech)','Reflow Operator','Reserve Tube Welder','Resistance Machine Welder Setter','Resistance Welding Machine Operator','Robotic Weld Operator','Robotic Weld Technician (Robotic Weld Tech)','Robotic Welder','Robotic Welding Operator','Rod Welder']::text[], ARRAY['Welding, Soldering, and Brazing Machine Setters, Operators, and